ComicInfo.Title: The End of Infinity!
ComicInfo.Summary: The End of Infinity!: Thor learns the secret of Infinity. It is Odin himself! In a scheme hatched by Hela, Odin must battle Odin. Odin prevails, of course, but in doing so, he had to strike a deal with Hela. Her price? The life of Thor!
